        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-hazel-blears' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0417P2_20040130_CWS_1' title='Link to this speech by Ms Hazel Blears' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-hazel-blears" title="Ms Hazel Blears">The Minister for Crime Reduction, Policing and Community Safety (Ms Hazel Blears)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I have today placed in the Library a copy of the Police Grant Report (England and Wales) 2004&#x2013;05 (HC 277). The report sets out my determination for 2004&#x2013;05 of the aggregate amount of grants that I propose to pay under section 46(2) of the <a href="/acts/police-act-1996">Police Act 1996</a>, and the amount to be paid to each police authority and to the Greater London Authority for the Metropolitan Police Authority.</p><p>Allocations for each police authority for financial years 2003&#x2013;04 and 2004&#x2013;05 are set out in the table:
